org.neo4j.helpers.collection
Class CollectionWrapper<T,U>

java.lang.Object
  org.neo4j.helpers.collection.CollectionWrapper<T,U>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of items
U - the type of items of the underlying/wrapped collection
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>, Collection<T>
public abstract class CollectionWrapper<T,U>
extends Object
implements Collection<T>

Wraps a Collection, making it look (and function) like a collection holding another type of items. The wrapper delegates to its underlying collection instead of keeping track of the items itself.
